properties.name: CreativeRHINO Home Base
properties.description: Posted by Creativerhino CreativeRHINO does have a home base that exists outside of the digital realm. It is far from the chatter of digital bytes. The stars shine brighter, blue herons cloud the skies, the water laps at the edges of land, and frogs peep into the night. Our Blackberrys go silent, the laptops close, our ears open to the world, and our minds fill with creative thoughts. Home sweet home.
